 drivers/iio/imu/inv_mpu6050/inv_mpu_iio.h  |  2 ++
 drivers/iio/imu/inv_mpu6050/inv_mpu_ring.c | 15 ++++++++++++---
 3 files changed, 23 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

